data.description: THE LYNNATRA! This 1.5 level David Weekley Energy Saver Home sits on a tree-lined home site and is located in a gated community with easy access to abundant nature trails. THE LYNNATRA boasts a large open floor plan with 3/2.5/2, including an upstairs bonus room that is perfect for entertaining, a conveniently situated home office, and much more! Call today for information on THE LYNNATRA! Brokered And Advertised By: David Weekley Homes, Inc. Listing Agent: Jimmy Rado
